name: Extreme Australian Animal Warfare Simulator (D-INFK GameJam 2022)

description: A game DarkPhoton and I made for the D-INFK GameJam (2022). The theme was Australia and we decided to make a Plants-vs-Zombies-like game where you fight australian wildlife.
